  "properties": {
    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "##  🔍Teacher Tip\r\nStudents will see each of these levels separately. We've combined here them for a more streamlined PL experience. \r\nAs you prompt, notice how the responses change at each level of context provided.\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; background-color: #F5F7F8; padding: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #8148B2; display: inline-block;\">➡️ This activity is from Lesson 3. You can find more details in the full <a href='https://studio.code.org/s/aif1-2025/lessons/3' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer' style='text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;'>Lesson Plan</a>.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Travel Agent - Minimal Context Given\r\n\r\nPractice prompting through the career of a travel agent by giving a simple, unstructured prompt to see how AI makes recommendations without any specific details or examples.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Try a basic prompt like the one below, or a similar one related to family vacations.\r\n\r\n>Recommend a family vacation destination.\r\n\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how useful or generic the recommendation is.\r\n\r\n---\r\n## Travel Agent - Providing a Single Example\r\n\r\nPractice prompting through the career of a travel agent by adding a single example to help guide the AI's recommendation.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Prompt AI to recommend a family destination by including **an example** vacation destination.\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how the AI builds on your example to make a more specific or relevant suggestion.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure where to start?**]\r\nHere's an example prompt:\r\n> Recommend a vacation destination for a family of four that enjoys outdoor adventures and cultural experiences. For example: \r\n>\r\n> \"The Bahamas offers beautiful beaches and family-friendly resorts.\" \r\n:::\r\n\r\n---\r\n## Travel Agent - Providing Multiple Examples\r\n\r\nPractice prompting through the career of a travel agent by giving the AI a detailed and structured request that includes multiple expectations.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Prompt AI to recommend a family destination by including **several examples** vacation destination.\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how the added context improves the accuracy, relevance, and usefulness of the recommendation.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure where to start?**]\r\nHere's an example prompt:\r\n> Recommend a vacation destination for a family of four that enjoys outdoor adventures and cultural experiences. For example: \r\n>\r\n> \"The Bahamas offers beautiful beaches and family-friendly resorts.\" \r\n>\r\n> OR\r\n> \r\n> \"Palm Springs offers many nearby hiking opportunities and mini-golf adventures.\"\r\n>\r\n> OR\r\n> \r\n> \"Thailand offers jungle excursions and lunar themed parties.\"\r\n:::",
